The tutorial and assignment count is not stored after
executing config command.

This change include
- A default count number so that the test cases
  do not fail because of arrays of length 0.
- Store the count values inside preference.json, and it is loaded
  when every the app starts.
- Made the trackers not immutable to allow for change in size.
